name: V̵i̸j̵h̸a̸r̵h̴u̵n̵a̷ - the sitting paradox
description:
ॐ नमः शिवाय,
;
2480 x 3508 portrait of the act of 
sitting down, performed by vijharhuna,
a kmiuic._9 system entity considered
the only one to engage upon stillness
for the longest timespace period. The
attached mind, creates the sub-nirvanic
paths elevated by its own aura. Once initiated,
it will carry on its telephatic influence
till eternal ether expands a new life in another
dimensional tunnel. Till then, it remains still, 
yet its mind in chaotic bio-bloom, fertile and 
systematic.
